        <h2  class="recipe" id="pancakes">Pancakes</h2>
        
        <ul>
            <li>Difficulty: 5/10</li>
            <li>Clean up: 6/10</li>
            <li>Taste: sweet and savoury</li>
            <li>Time: 60 minutes</li>
            <li>Serves: 5 people</li>
        </ul>
        
        <table id="ingredientsPancakes">
            <thead>
                <tr>
                    <th>Ingredients</th>
                    <th>Quantity</th>
                </tr>
            </thead>
            <tbody>
                <tr>
                    <td>Flour</td>
                    <td>1 cup</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td>Milk</td>
                    <td>1 cup</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td>Egg</td>
                    <td>1</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td>Baking soda</td>
                    <td>1 teaspoon</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td>salt</td>
                    <td>1 teaspoon</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td>Flour</td>
                    <td>1 cup</td>
                </tr>
            </tbody>
        </table>
        
        <h3 id="stepsPancakes" class="steps">Steps:</h3>
        <ol class="steps">
            <li>Put all the dry stuff in a bowl</li>
            <li>Mix it all together rly well</li>
            <li>Make a well in the middle of it</li>
            <li>Pour the milk inside the well</li>
            <li>Beat the egg in a seperate bowl</li>
            <li>Put the egg in the well too</li>
            <li>Mix and thats your batter</li>
            <li>Pour 1/4 cup of batter on buttered pan</li>                 <li>When small bubbles pop flip</li>
            <li>cook for 1.5 min</li>
            <li>Take off pan and serve</li>
        </ol>
        
